# Discord Rich Presence for [Insomnia](https://insomnia.rest/)
This Insomnia plugin provides [Discord Rich Presence](https://discord.com/rich-presence) support for Insomnia.

![demo](https://owo.whats-th.is/2rLFhm8.png)

# Installation
1. Open your preferences in Insomnia
2. Type `insomnia-plugin-discord-rich-presence`
3. Click `Install Plugin`

# Notes
The URL you are working on is not displayed for security reasons. The information displayed is the method, the response code, and whatever you have called your request.
